<DESCRIPTION>JKs, i'g'r' photometry of C stars in NGC 6822 (Demers+, 2006)</DESCRIPTION>
<DESCRIPTION>Positions, JKs and SLOAN photometry of  C stars</DESCRIPTION>
<!-- Positions, JKs and SLOAN photometry of C stars {\em(tables 2 and 3 of paper)} -->
<!-- +++No column could be found to attach a LINK in table: J/A+A/456/905/Cstars -->
<DESCRIPTION>? Number from Letarte et al. (2002, Cat. <J/AJ/123/832>) [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="RAJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.ra;meta.main" ref="J2000" datatype="char" arraysize="11" unit="'h:m:s'"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_RA_MAIN" -->
<FIELD name="DEJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.dec;meta.main" ref="J2000" datatype="char" arraysize="11" unit="'d:m:s'"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_DEC_MAIN" -->
<FIELD name="Ksmag" ucd="phot.mag;em.IR.K" datatype="float" width="6" precision="3"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_K" -->
<FIELD name="J-Ks" ucd="phot.color;em.IR.J;em.IR.K" datatype="float" width="6" precision="3"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_J-K" -->
<FIELD name="e_J-Ks" ucd="stat.error" datatype="float" width="6" precision="3"><!-- ucd="ERROR" -->
